description: This table represents details of Medicaid (coverage for Adults). Medicaid provides free health insurance for low-income adults. Eligible adults receive their medical care through a managed care plan or fee-for-service. While your application is being processed, Medicaid may provide up to 90 days of retroactive coverage for unpaid medical bills, if you are eligible during those 90 days.
